content.title: Casio Black Out
content.top_review:
This is one of Casio's best. I have two with the silver LCD displays, and one with the black. Black display is sleek and modern, but a bit harder to read, naturally, than the silver ones. But that's my choice -- in this case, fashion over function. Best part of this watch is the 24-hour DUAL TIME display function -- my second time is always set to GMT in 24-hour format, which I use for work every day. It's also extremely comfortable, lightweight, waterproof and tough. I literally wash it gently with soap and water after a long run or bike ride. Five stars overall -- value for money, function and durability. Caveat for the black display only; slightly harder to read.
  
Read more
content.description: The Casio Men's Classic Digital Sport Watch features an intuitive design that makes it easy-to-use for on-the-go athletes. The timepiece is constructed with a durable resin case, a stationary black resin bezel, and a black resin band with an adjustable buckle clasp. A durable mineral window shields the square digital-blacked out dial face, which features a digital time display along with the day, date, and month. The watch also includes light, mode, and adjust buttons that allow you to personalize your watch display to suit your workout. The digital-quartz-powered timepiece is water resistant to 330 feet.
